   "question": "Where does Restoration Druid Phase 3 BiS come from?",
   "answer": "From the gear worn by 263 top-ranked Restoration Druid healing parses on Warcraft Logs during Phase 3 (Black Temple and Mount Hyjal), aggregated per slot — what high parsers actually equip, not a spreadsheet ideal."
  },
  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Restoration Druid items in Phase 3?",
   "answer": "Nordrassil Chestguard (85%), Nordrassil Life-Mantle (75%), Sunshower Light Cloak (71%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
  },
  {
   "question": "Should I follow this list exactly for Phase 3?",
